         I was thinking on a way to do it and this is what came to my mind:</P><P>1st step is to break the room, two ways i can think of to do that:</P><P>1 - IVU and stand in front of room then cast Charm and hope you can channel it and get one as your pet.</P><P>2 - Park a pet in the hallway, ST one of them and run back to pet hitting pet back off hotkey until pet is out of the sight from inside the room, then fight one at a time. Remember that ST have a high chance of mem blurring static mobs. </P><P>2nd step after room is broke is how am i going to kill the AM when it pops:</P><P>1 - Only way i can think of is sticking pet on it, slowing the thing, then BoD and heal pet with Shadow compact often. Probably Asystole would be good here cause of the debuffs and Ignite blood for the high dmg.</P><P>That's how i am going to try tonight.</P><P>Any ideas?</P><P>Onail Aeroc<BR>49 Necromancer<BR>Aei'Desis for life<BR>Xegony</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
